Package: VSHunter
Title: Capture Variation Signatures from Genomic Data
Description: Identify copy number signatures from distribution of copy number 
    features and mutation signatures from MAF 
    for enabling the interpretation of complex genomic changes in cancer.
Version: 0.5.1
